无法破坏例子，给玩家无法破坏的钻石剑:
/give @a diamond_sword 1 0 {Unbreakable:1b}
属性例子，给玩家拿着会增加20攻击力的钻石剑:/give @a diamond_sword 1 0 {AttributeModifiers:[{Operation:0,UUIDLeast:1,UUIDMost:1,AttributeName:"generic.attackDamage",Amount:20,Name:"123",Slot:"Head"}]}
这个帖子对于高版本也大概是适用的,只不过差了个slot
附魔例子，给玩家附魔锋利7的钻石剑:
/give @a diamond_sword 1 0 {ench:[{id:16,lvl:7}]}
id在这里找https://minecraft-zh.gamepedia.com/%E9%99%84%E9%AD%94
